{"tid":449581,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"男人摸女人叫非禮，女人摸女人點解又得？","createTime":"2017-10-27T10:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T11:29:08.000Z","uid":148011,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f3c502fc7f344b39ea0a04d37cd7e8a63a8f4fd8","tid":449581,"uid":148011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:13:55.000Z","msg":"成日喺繁忙時間搭地鐵，好逼好多人，貼埋少少都好難避免。<br />\n<br />\n通常啲男人都會避忌，就算喺金鐘人貼人咁都盡量唔會掂到啲女人，驚比人嗌非禮。<br />\n<br />\n但啲女人，特別係呀嬸師奶，佢地持住自己係女人真係肆無忌憚咁出手非禮人。成日比呀嬸出手推手臂，背脊，腰同patpat。<br />\n<br />\n兼且佢地完全覺得同人肉貼肉係無問題，試過比啲呀嬸全程用手臂貼住我個胸，又試過patpat痴實patpat(壓到個蘿扁嗰隻)。<br />\n<br />\n就算大家都係女人都唔代表我個身可以比人摸，我亦都唔想摸你對核突墜波。希望香港可以有再清晰啲既法例列明，女人摸女人同男人摸女人一樣都係犯法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4092b77c6df7a133c7f17fb8d976b742d801f32b","tid":449581,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a1dde8e437780bd8a65403f8e75aae6b4912bce","tid":449581,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:15:59.000Z","msg":"驚既買架私家車或者搭的士，再唔係搵NASA返火星，地球很危險"},{"pid":"113b9eb2a88a145d1332e505a0afec63cb827f7d","tid":449581,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:16:54.000Z","msg":"連登仔：因為所有女人都係雞"},{"pid":"7986735e3527bffac42dcfea66d8346787adb69f","tid":449581,"uid":139473,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男同女我都唔介意佢哋摸我</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc44da407a4a13ecfe7352ea7ca7cecd075d812","tid":449581,"uid":148011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>驚既買架私家車或者搭的士，再唔係搵NASA返火星，地球很危險</blockquote><br />\n唔係驚比人唔小心撞到，或者逼到，係有心出手摸嗰隻摸。<br />\n你啲削足適履既道理，乜連仔依家得翻啲咁既質素咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fcfea4f7097536c008ac8305a9345894e2adfff","tid":449581,"uid":148011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:52:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男同女我都唔介意佢哋摸我</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以幫我改錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  很想要"},{"pid":"cd4d517f6d3cfbb2a0dfcbfa398bc8fcc3830b87","tid":449581,"uid":28908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"你以為人地摸你 其實人地都覺得你摸緊佢"},{"pid":"4391623904b43c6b473f180566b00074c343d429","tid":449581,"uid":41737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T10:57:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f1a7e69273556e6b2a6897cb9dd94aa8aa33db3","tid":449581,"uid":148011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:18:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好成日發癲啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> A0死中女 日撚日係到ff有人想摸你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底你真人係咪唔會出街 ？ 隱青果堆？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> on9死毒撚"},{"pid":"616d44825c7d5df5f7ba2d8e0a3002b35b5b269f","tid":449581,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:25:30.000Z","msg":"樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勿摸樓主"},{"pid":"3eb49e1ca84f1da4b015a367f2d036170153a557","tid":449581,"uid":148011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T11:29:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勿摸樓主</blockquote><br />\n就算全世界女人都係雞，但都仲未有連登仔份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}